{"tid":2394256,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"知己一聲拜拜放棄這都市 - 林夕","createTime":"2021-02-04T05:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T03:16:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b156e4451876ee1c410d181e8daf17ae184c86a9","tid":2394256,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:06:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210204/ESCP7X5V5ZCVZOUDU7HOVJQGEY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210204%2FESCP7X5V5ZCVZOUDU7HOVJQGEY%2F&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRBkIbV9%2FoY%2BmeTBoP0X2IjM%3D&h=629e705d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210204%2FESCP7X5V5ZCVZOUDU7HOVJQGEY%2F&h=cae07ea8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210204/ESCP7X5V5ZCVZOUDU7HOVJQGEY/</a><br />\n<br />\n知己一聲拜拜放棄這都市 - 林夕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GYYG0Cii_8SvipoV_DVQxlrA1lI=/1261x859/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZEFSA47EXRAQ7IOBH2VEU3HHA4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGYYG0Cii_8SvipoV_DVQxlrA1lI%3D%2F1261x859%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZEFSA47EXRAQ7IOBH2VEU3HHA4.png&h=5221c982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1990年，第一代歌神寫〈同舟共濟〉，同時又創作〈話知你九七〉。一年後，不知第幾代的螺絲釘填詞人寫了〈皇后大道東〉。歌神在九七來臨前，啓示港人「未有耐到97，拿起枝筆數下二千零廿八日（駛乜急）」。在諸神已近黃昏的時代，我只想做一個人。這個人也不必看遍了中國近代史，光是有個廣州親戚，無端端有人火熱中送炭，要跪在上面，之後餘生要坐輪椅，試問如何不急？<br />\n<br />\n〈皇后大道東〉剛面世，在大陸立地成禁歌。螺絲釘填詞人捫心自問，寫了什麼會變禁忌？擔憂前景，不只政權轉移，大陸同胞同志們面臨光盤政策，身為一個大胃王外食怕會被舉報，正常過教師怕被同事打小報告。<br />\n<br />\n如今自我檢討，終於懂得默寫了認罪書。首先，「有個貴族朋友，在硬幣背後，青春不變名字叫做皇后。每次買賣隨我到處去奔走，面上沒有表情卻匯聚成就。」快回歸了啊，榮光不歸於黨，還敢說硬幣上的英女皇是貴族，沒有表情地積極不干預政策可以匯聚成就？跟她攀關係裝熟稱之為朋友，在後面一段還敢說：「這個正義朋友面善又友善，因此批准馬匹一周跑兩天」，覺得萬惡殖民帝國主義者友善，又代表正義，那麼，「要搞搞新意思」的「偉大同志」又算什麼？<br />\n<br />\n當時有愚民說歌詞像一則預言。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n錯了就要認，罰就要企定。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n螺絲釘填詞人自知在這個詞的罪名叫「懷緬過去常陶醉」，在「一半樂事，一半令人流淚」的回憶裏，唯一悔過是，寫到「知己一聲拜拜，遠去這都市」已覺得把「遠去」當「及物動詞」不自然，也絕不準確，待到歌曲派台，才想起要改為「知己一聲拜拜放棄這都市」，多傳神。悔不該當時為了江湖救急，一鬆手交出「遠去」，放棄了想到用「放棄」的機會。跟所有香港人一樣，當時沒拼盡全力守護專業精神，如今悔之晚矣。"},{"pid":"e368cb244246df5d24a3da9ca0d711d5d325be9d","tid":2394256,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befb9c815f8b2ae847ed12001dd08626805277d4","tid":2394256,"uid":61181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:09:53.000Z","msg":"首都呢隻碟先係預言曲<br />\n<br />\n聽下一隻叫新生代既歌<br />\n完全係呢幾年既寫照<br />\n點解夕爺咁勁<br />\n廿鳩幾年前已經預視到所有野<br />\n<br />\n新生代<br />\n<br />\n作詞：林夕<br />\n作曲：羅大佑<br />\n<br />\n從各方刀光劍影裡誕生<br />\n別了溫室的安定氣溫<br />\n雛生的一雙耳慣聽機密<br />\n剛張開兩眼便見證史實<br />\n遊戲老師解說怎叫上街<br />\n就算彼此都不太瞭解<br />\n娃娃的一雙腳太快長大<br />\n走得出過去避免再失敗<br />\n<br />\n我要作優質新生代<br />\n爸媽的苦惱給我解開<br />\n我會是精英新生代<br />\n我努力翻江覆雨倒海<br />\n<br />\n遊戲規則將變得更簡單<br />\n活躍於忠奸底線之間<br />\n忽東忽西轉變次數不限<br />\n不必公證勝負太過短暫<br />\n<br />\n傳說裡的感覺早已作古<br />\n健教書講解怎去吃苦<br />\n苦海中找不到救世的父<br />\n孤雛都會靠自我去保護<br />\n<br />\n永遠是標準新生代<br />\n爸媽的苦惱給我解開<br />\n我已是尖端新生代<br />\n我要為他朝開創風采<br />\n<br />\n微笑嘆息都已收進唱片<br />\n電腦畫面中追溯祖先<br />\n青春的滄桑客滿腦經驗<br />\n春秋的對錯時間會分辨<br />\n年老的當天誕生了今天<br />\n在這天青春找到昨天<br />\n光影中新主角快要出現<br />\n高速演變我們過去的臉"},{"pid":"1b5854cb53e62b80110e7a8ef63333514bc0828f","tid":2394256,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e546baa21175ca7f7d90c3906ef8f230a6ba50","tid":2394256,"uid":61181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:13:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/by2ZiXRHzr8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fby2ZiXRHzr8&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRBkIbV9%2FoY%2BmeTBoP0X2IjM%3D&h=f2ecd223\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/by2ZiXRHzr8</a>"},{"pid":"9b5f8898147ff28feabe345b7cc2feabd587af2d","tid":2394256,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:18:51.000Z","msg":"攞到BNO 5+1 Visa 啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2395051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2395051</a>"},{"pid":"0bfdeefaa7f900f0431520044b9a3b16d06c8f68","tid":2394256,"uid":161711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"1983 許冠傑 洋紫荊 <br />\n<br />\n唏噓&hellip;&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ebe85b7cff785d44c8e050333636f72c3f02c6","tid":2394256,"uid":282359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41e546baa21175ca7f7d90c3906ef8f230a6ba50","tid":2394256,"uid":61181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:13:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/by2ZiXRHzr8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fby2ZiXRHzr8&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRBkIbV9%2FoY%2BmeTBoP0X2IjM%3D&h=f2ecd223\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/by2ZiXRHzr8</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T17:34:53.000Z","msg":"嘩正！未聽過。好正！<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e496bec3dda382ad4d4f86e9b9aa6859ed214996","tid":2394256,"uid":282359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T17:35:29.000Z","msg":"最啱都係呢句：若做大國公民只需身有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f298a053c3cc9a10d95249327f6132acf6d140f1","tid":2394256,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T17:39:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">夕爺終於講出事實<br />\n大家已經盡力，完全唔需要慚愧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/